c: 38
v: 26
t: "Hini na Dâwûd! Inene wena Sikubekele ukuba ube ngummeli ehlabathini; ngoko ke gweba ngokusenyanisweni, ungalandeli iminqweno yakho ngokuba iya kukuphambukisa eNdleleni ka-Allâh Inene abo baphambukayo eNdleleni ka-Allâh baya kufumana isohlwayo esibuhlungu ngokuba bona baye balibala ngeMini yemibuzo"